title: Chermoula Chicken & Jewelled Rice with Lemon Yoghurt & Flaked Almonds
description: Add a little sparkle to your weeknight dinner with this bright and richly flavoured chicken meal. The “jewels” in the colourful rice
are lightly cooked greens, roasted beetroot and plump currants, creating an easy and addictive dish that will steal your heart.

